trans-unit.source: Defines several color palettes that are commonly used by bitmap images.
trans-unit.target: Define várias paletas de cores que são normalmente usadas por imagens de bitmap.

trans-unit.source: BitmapPalettes properties whose names end with "Transparent" have an additional "color" that is fully transparent.
trans-unit.target: BitmapPalettes propriedades cujos nomes terminam com "Transparente" ter adicional "cores" que é totalmente transparente.

trans-unit.source: In the case of palettes that already have 256 colors, the last color is replaced by the transparent color.
trans-unit.target: No caso de paletas que já têm 256 cores, a última cor é substituída por cor transparente.

trans-unit.source: Only [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gif](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-gif-md.md)] image formats support palettes.
trans-unit.target: Somente [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_tiff](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-tiff-md.md)] e [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gif](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-gif-md.md)] paletas de suporte de formatos de imagem.
